class=\"mtk12\">on</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Done&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">‚ùØ‚óØ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">the</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Google</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Analytics</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">tracking</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">script</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ‚óØ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">responsive</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">images</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ‚óâ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">an</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">automatic</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">sitemap</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ‚óØ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Generate</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">manifest</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">file</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ‚óâ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Markdown</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">and</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">MDX</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">support</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ‚óØ </span><span class=\"mtk12